flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Completion of battery/drive unit final inspection.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawler - Retrieve final inspection results from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Remote Functions - Evaluate inspection results and approve/reject units.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Remote Functions - Determine optimal storage locations and rotation.]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: Remote Functions - Define packaging and labeling strategies.]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Remote Functions - Plan and schedule outbound loads.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Remote Functions - Generate shipment documentation and ensure customs compliance.]
  N6 --> N7{Decision: Approve or reject final inspections, determine storage locations, packaging/labeling strategies, load planning, and shipment documentation.}
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced handling costs, minimized stockouts, improved on-time delivery, and accelerated order fulfillment.]
  N7 -->|Final inspection fails.| B1[Reject units and initiate re-inspection process.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Units are held for re-inspection.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Insufficient storage space available.| B2[Allocate temporary storage and adjust rotation strategy.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Temporary storage is utilized to manage inventory.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Cross-border regulations change.| B3[Update documentation templates and compliance checks.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Updated documentation ensures ongoing compliance.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]